title: "The Legend of Oni" Club/ Clan looking for active ppl to play! Everyone can join!

embed.description: Yatesu / Gold 3 0LP / 49W 60L Win Ratio 45% / Vayne - 31W 24L Win Ratio 56%, Jinx - 26W 15L Win Ratio 63%, Ezreal - 11W 11L Win Ratio 50%, Yasuo - 10W 12L Win Ratio 45%, Jhin - 10W 11L Win Ratio 48%

body:
If u are an active player and u have fun of playing LoL then join our Club/ Clan! 
There is also a Discord for our Club/ Clan so u can find some ppl to play or just chat with someone!
If u want to join us then add me in LoL and write me a message so I can invite u and tell u the details :)

EUW: Yatesu


What u need to join:
- be friendly
- be active
- have fun
- be communicative
